    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.97) * wp.abs(0.41))
    v2 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = (v0 + wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.98)))
    v1 = (tmp / (0.61 + (tmp + 0.96 + v0 + 0.24)))
    v2 = 0.61
    tmp = (tmp - 0.31)
    data[tid] = v0
